OL,3,CWhat is the birth trauma inquiry and
OL,4,Chow can I submit evidence?
OL,6,FThe inquiry's aim is to investigate
OL,7,Fthe causes of birth trauma and was
OL,8,Flaunched by Stafford Conservative MP
OL,9,FTheo Clarke after she needed emergency
OL,10,Fsurgery during the birth of her
OL,11,Fdaughter in 2022.
OL,13,FThe Birth Trauma Association estimates
OL,14,Fthat 25,000 to 30,000 women experience
OL,15,FPTSD after birth in the UK, and its
OL,16,Fhoped the inquiry will help form
OL,17,Fpolicy recommendations for the
OL,18,FGovernment to reduce these numbers
