OL,3,CWhat is the birth trauma inquiry and
OL,4,Chow can I submit evidence?
OL,6,FThe inquiry was originally accepting
OL,7,Fwritten and oral testimonies until
OL,8,FTuesday 6 February, but the
OL,9,Foverwhelming number of submissions has
OL,10,Fcaused the deadline to be extended to
OL,11,F20 February.
OL,13,FWhat is birth trauma?
OL,15,FThe inquiry's request for personal
OL,16,Fexperiences outlines what could be
OL,17,Fconsidered as "birth trauma".
