OL,3,CWhat is the birth trauma inquiry and
OL,4,Chow can I submit evidence?
OL,6,FWhile the inquiry outlines these
OL,7,Fexperiences and symptoms, it also
OL,8,Fstresses that no two cases of birth
OL,9,Ftrauma are the same and encourages
OL,10,Fpeople to still submit testimonies
OL,11,Feven if their exact case is not
OL,12,Freflected in their guidelines.
OL,14,FHow do I submit my testimony?
OL,16,FWritten testimonies should be emailed
OL,17,Fas a word document to
OL,18,Finquiry@birthtraumaassociation.org.uk.
