OL,3,CWhat is the birth trauma inquiry and
OL,4,Chow can I submit evidence?
OL,6,FThe inquiry asks for personal accounts
OL,7,Fof direct experiences with birth
OL,8,Ftrauma, and also encourages people to
OL,9,Fmention positive moments so that they
OL,10,Fwill understand what does work.
OL,12,FIt is recommended your testimony is no
OL,13,Flonger than 1,500 words and anonymous
OL,14,Ftestimonies are also accepted.
