OL,3,CWhat is the birth trauma inquiry and
OL,4,Chow can I submit evidence?
OL,6,FAn NHS spokesperson said: "The NHS is
OL,7,Fimproving our support to women who
OL,8,Fhave experienced a traumatic birth
OL,9,Fthrough rolling out specialist
OL,10,Fcommunity perinatal teams and offering
OL,11,Fcomprehensive postnatal check-ups.
OL,13,F"But we understand there is more to
OL,14,Fdo, which is why the NHS is investing
OL,15,F#186 million to hire more midwives and
OL,16,Fother clinicians, backed by a three-
OL,17,Fyear delivery plan for maternity and
OL,18,Fneonatal services which will make care
OL,19,Fsafer and more personalised for women
OL,20,Fand babies."
